HEADWORD: Mawk
<hw>Mawk</hw> <pr>(m⟦add⟧k)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>mauk</ets>, <ets>ma⟦edh⟧ek</ets>, Icel. <ets>ma⟦edh⟧kr</ets>; akin
